Trade/Device Name(s): ELITech Clinical Systems URINE TOTAL PROTEIN Standard 100 mg/dL
ELITech Clinical Systems URINE CONTROL BI-LEVEL
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): ELITech Clinical Systems Selectra Pro Series Analyzers
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for ELITech Clinical Systems urine total protein standard calibrator and urine control bi-level for use on Selectra Pro Series analyzers.
Indications for Use Summary: Calibrator is for calibration of quantitative urine total protein; control is a bi-level urine quality control, both used with ELITech Clinical Systems Selectra Pro Series Analyzers.
